=== Three dimensions ===
The Clifford algebra Cℓ3,0(formula_11) is built up from a basis of one unit scalar, 1, three orthogonal unit vectors, &quot;σ&quot;1, &quot;σ&quot;2 and &quot;σ&quot;3, the three unit bivectors &quot;σ&quot;1&quot;σ&quot;2, &quot;σ&quot;2&quot;σ&quot;3, &quot;σ&quot;3&quot;σ&quot;1 and the pseudoscalar . It is straightforward to show that , and .

